msgid "Cloning from Version Control"
msgstr ""

# cb7c38668ab24aeeaea41274f5baf515
#: ../../admin-guide/installation/index.en.rst:84
msgid ""
"|TS| uses a `public Git repository <https://git-wip-"
"us.apache.org/repos/asf/trafficserver.git>`_ for version control. This "
"repository will also provide the most cutting edge source code if you "
"wish to test out the latest features and bug fixes."
msgstr ""

# c63d02a26d404f589521d5d66f0a01fb
#: ../../admin-guide/installation/index.en.rst:90
msgid ""
"We do also have a `GitHub Mirror "
"<https://github.com/apache/trafficserver>`_ that you may use to submit "
"pull requests. However, it may not be entirely up-to-date, and you should"
" always refer to our official project Git repository for the very latest "
"state of the source code."
msgstr ""

